@startuml
left to right direction

actor "User" as User

rectangle "Traffic Camera Browser" {

  boundary "Map & Camera Viewer UI\n<<boundary>>" as B1
  control "Live Stream Controller\n<<control>>" as C1
  entity "Camera Catalog\n<<entity>>" as E1
  entity "Live Stream Session\n<<entity>>" as E2
}

note right of B1
  The platform displays a map showing
  the location of each camera. Users
  can watch videos by clicking on the
  corresponding camera.
end note

User --> B1 : click camera on map
B1 --> C1 : request live stream
C1 --> E1 : fetch camera stream URL
C1 --> E2 : start/track session
C1 --> B1 : deliver live video

@enduml